  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网设备接入的流程图。核心节点是MQTT Broker，它是整个系统的入口。然后边缘节点EdgeNode负责实际的数据采集，TelemetryStream代表数据流。我想让流程体现设备从注册到验证的完整状态流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Broker作为入口。那状态流转的具体顺序是什么？EdgeNode是直接从Broker获取验证，还是中间有TelemetryStream的参与？另外pendingApproval和pendingConfirmation这两个状态是独立的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "流程是这样的：设备先连上Broker（thanksSigningUp状态），然后需要验证（thanksVerifying）。验证通过后进入pendingApproval等待审批。但还有个分支——Broker也可以直接让某些设备进入pendingConfirmation待确认状态，这个待确认状态最终还是要回到验证环节。验证通过后再到审批。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下：Broker（thanksSigningUp）有两条出边，一条到EdgeNode的验证（thanksVerifying），另一条直接到pendingConfirmation。然后pendingConfirmation要回到thanksVerifying，验证通过后再到pendingApproval。这样pendingApproval就是终点状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "pendingApproval"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，pendingApproval是终点。另外注意pendingConfirmation和pendingApproval虽然都是TelemetryStream的实例，但它们是不同的状态节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "pendingApproval",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画一版：四个节点——Broker（thanksSigningUp）、EdgeNode（thanksVerifying）、两个TelemetryStream状态（pendingApproval和pendingConfirmation）。连线按你说的：Broker到验证、Broker到待确认、验证到审批、待确认回到验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，pendingConfirmation回到的是thanksVerifying，不是直接到pendingApproval。你刚才说的\"待确认回到验证\"是对的，但让我确认一下连线方向——pendingConfirmation -- thanksVerifying，然后thanksVerifying -- pendingApproval。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，修正：pendingConfirmation指向thanksVerifying，验证通过后再到pendingApproval。这样整个闭环就完整了——Broker分流，验证汇聚，最终统一进入审批状态。我这就定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "thanksSigningUp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
